abstract: NHL Roundup; Tampa Bay Lightning defeat New York Islanders, 4-1; other NHL results noted.
snippet: The Islanders lost, 4-1, at Tampa Bay. Ryan McDonagh’s overtime goal lifted the Rangers past the Flames, 3-2.
